This Privacy Policy explains how Dobre Bot ("the Bot") handles your data.

1. Data We Collect

User IDs: Stored for inventory tracking (K-pop boyfriend/girlfriend collections)

Command Logs: Timestamp, username, user ID, server name, channel name, and command used

Inventory Data: Your collected K-pop characters are saved locally in a JSON file

2. Data We Do NOT Collect

We do NOT store message content

We do NOT collect email addresses, passwords, or personal information

We do NOT record voice channel audio

3. How We Use Data

Inventory data: To display your collected K-pop characters when using /inventar

Command logs: For debugging and monitoring Bot usage

4. Data Storage

All data is stored locally on the Bot owner's computer

Data is NOT shared with third parties

Data is NOT sold or used for advertising

5. Data Retention

Inventory data is kept indefinitely unless you request deletion

Command logs are stored locally and may be cleared periodically

6. Your Rights

You may request deletion of your inventory data by contacting the Bot owner

You may request to view what data is stored about you

7. Children's Privacy

The Bot is not intended for users under 13 years of age

We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13

8. Changes

This policy may be updated at any time

Continued use of the Bot constitutes acceptance of any changes

9. Contact

For data requests or privacy concerns, contact: Bot owner via Discord

